These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-1::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: western, comedy
House: ranch-style, colonial
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: august, march
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: begonia, lily
1. the person watching western movies is on the far right##1
2. the person who's birthday is in august is on the right of the person who growslily##1
3. the ranch-style house is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |     2     |
| Movie-Genre       | comedy       | western |
| House         | colonial | ranch-style  |
| Birthday       | march    | august    |
| Flower   | lily       | begonia      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-2::.
2 different pets are kept: ferret, cat
The people use 2 different means of transport: helicopter, jet-ski
There are 2 different favourite colors: turquise, mauve
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: bongani, tiparillo
1. the person who likes turquise is on the right of the bongani-smoker##1
2. the person driving the helicopter is on the far left##1
3. the person who likes turquise is on the right of the owner of the cat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |      2      |
| Pet      | cat     | ferret |
| Transport           | helicopter | jet-ski      |
| Color   | mauve  | turquise      |
| Cigar         | bongani | tiparillo     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-3::.
There are 2 different nationalities: spanish, japanese
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: fantasy, animation
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: baseball, parkour
2 different games are played: bridge, billiard
1. the person who's sport is parkour is on the left of the japanese##1
2. the spanish is the person playing billiard##1
3. the person watching fantasy movies is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |
| Nationality      | spanish | japanese  |
| Movie-Genre          | fantasy    | animation   |
| Sport   | parkour  | baseball   |
| Game     | billiard     | bridge |

