City: boston, nizza
1. the person traveling to boston is on the far left##1
2. the person watching crime movies is on the right of the turkish##1
3. the pakistani is the dannemann-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |    2     |
| Nationality      | turkish       | pakistani |
| Cigar          | siglo         | dannemann    |
| Movie-Genre           | mystery | crime    |
| City   | boston           | nizza   |

