There 2 different types of food: asparagus, nectarine
City: edinburgh, colone
1. the montecristo-smoker is on the right of the person playing monopoly##1
2. the montecristo-smoker is on the right of the person traveling to colone##1
3. the person eating asparagus is the havana-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |     2     |
| Cigar           | havana | montecristo     |
| Game   | monopoly          | chess |
| Food           | asparagus          | nectarine    |
| City     | colone            | edinburgh       |

 